1
00:00:29,660 --> 00:00:34,620
♪Holding a sword that pierces nine heavens
I'm as carefree as I can be♪

2
00:00:35,380 --> 00:00:40,980
♪Not going to waste my youth while I'm young♪

3
00:00:41,140 --> 00:00:43,900
♪I slay demons at the end of the divine path♪

4
00:00:44,020 --> 00:00:46,860
♪I stop by Hell♪

5
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:52,940
♪I accept all challenges that come my way♪

6
00:00:53,340 --> 00:00:59,020
♪A young man with two lives♪

7
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:04,860
♪Roaming the martial world
hundreds of nations under his feet♪

8
00:01:05,140 --> 00:01:07,900
♪Had his bloodline awakened in a secret realm♪

9
00:01:07,980 --> 00:01:11,180
♪Refined his body from the inside
in thunderstorms♪

10
00:01:12,180 --> 00:01:16,500
♪A hero of the ancient world♪

11
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:20,060
♪Boiling hot human blood♪

12
00:01:20,380 --> 00:01:23,100
♪His hand stretches through space♪

13
00:01:23,300 --> 00:01:28,260
♪Which fighter will make it to the top?♪

14
00:01:28,460 --> 00:01:34,140
♪In the 33rd realm
he'll be slashing the great sky♪

15
00:01:34,740 --> 00:01:37,540
♪That's me, a living legend♪

16
00:01:37,540 --> 00:01:41,900
[Dominator of Martial Gods]

17
00:01:46,300 --> 00:01:49,220
[Episode 01]

18
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,950
[With the Demon Clan going rogue,]

19
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:59,400
[the Martial Domain descended into chaos.]

20
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:02,400
[Qin Chen, Martial God of the Martial Domain]
[A Supreme God named Qin Chen came down]

21
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,350
[Qin Chen, Martial God of the Martial Domain]

22
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:05,280
[to the Martial Domain
to fight against evil and preserve the good,]

23
00:02:06,510 --> 00:02:08,280
[ridding the world of the demons.]

24
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:14,120
[He was later revered as]

25
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,190
[the Martial God.]

26
00:02:37,380 --> 00:02:40,100
[Nine Heavens, Martial Domain]

27
00:02:57,300 --> 00:02:59,860
[Shangguan Xi'er,
Supreme God of the Martial Domain]

28
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:03,320
We talk in the moonlight.

29
00:03:04,670 --> 00:03:07,720
Together forever,

30
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:12,910
and may we never be apart.

31
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:25,510
Chen.

32
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:26,510
Xi'er,

33
00:03:28,070 --> 00:03:29,000
what do you think

34
00:03:30,230 --> 00:03:31,470
the Heavenly Way

35
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,190
is all about?

36
00:03:35,190 --> 00:03:37,190
The sun, the moon, and you.

37
00:03:38,230 --> 00:03:39,040
The sun represents the day.

38
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:40,440
The moon represents night.

39
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,510
You and I are just like day and night.

40
00:03:44,790 --> 00:03:47,070
I just want to be with you forever, Chen.

41
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:49,440
I couldn't care less about the Heavenly Way.

42
00:03:51,350 --> 00:03:52,160
The Heavenly Way…

43
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,720
is a gift from Heaven.

44
00:03:57,160 --> 00:04:00,470
It's intended to let us feel every living being

45
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:03,630
while being in this circle of life and death.

46
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,470
Chen,

47
00:04:07,350 --> 00:04:09,000
we are lords of the Martial Domain.

48
00:04:10,070 --> 00:04:12,040
What do those mortal beings' life and death,

49
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:13,160
emotions and feelings

50
00:04:13,510 --> 00:04:14,750
have to do with us anyway?

51
00:04:15,670 --> 00:04:16,400
Xi'er,

52
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:18,760
you don't get it.

53
00:04:27,310 --> 00:04:28,640
Existence is suffering.

54
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:35,200
Take these petals, for example.

55
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:39,520
After blooming,

56
00:04:40,790 --> 00:04:42,470
flowers will die shortly thereafter.

57
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:55,640
Xi'er,

58
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,550
we…

59
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:08,400
Xi'er…

60
00:05:10,230 --> 00:05:10,840
You…

61
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,470
Don't blame me for this,

62
00:05:14,110 --> 00:05:15,040
Chen.

63
00:05:15,430 --> 00:05:16,040
Why?

64
00:05:16,910 --> 00:05:17,790
Why?

65
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,960
Are you seriously asking me that?

66
00:05:24,110 --> 00:05:25,840
You don't understand me at all.

67
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:39,350
Xi'er,

68
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,040
what did I do

69
00:05:42,430 --> 00:05:43,520
to deserve this?

70
00:05:51,620 --> 00:05:54,220
[Feng Shaoyu, Supreme God of the Martial Domain]

71
00:05:55,310 --> 00:05:56,280
Shaoyu?

72
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:38,550
Wind, thunder, swords, river!

73
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:55,280
Let me give you a taste of this Seal of Galaxy!

74
00:07:13,790 --> 00:07:14,640
Chen,

75
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:16,280
you may be an accomplished cultivator,

76
00:07:16,470 --> 00:07:18,160
but you have your back to the wall now!

77
00:08:19,670 --> 00:08:21,200
Martial God,

78
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,720
descend!

79
00:08:56,790 --> 00:08:57,430
Chen,

80
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,670
you have been fatally poisoned.

81
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:02,240
Stripped of all your power.

82
00:09:03,190 --> 00:09:04,910
If I were you, I'd give up the fight.

83
00:09:29,430 --> 00:09:31,430
It'll take more than this

84
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:34,160
to contain me!

85
00:09:35,830 --> 00:09:37,760
Heavenly Spirit…

86
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:44,670
break!

87
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:56,640
Xi'er,

88
00:09:56,810 --> 00:09:57,600
don't let him get away!

89
00:09:58,090 --> 00:09:58,600
Go!

90
00:10:23,600 --> 00:10:24,480
Chen,

91
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,240
there's no escape from this,

92
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:28,990
no matter how hard you try.

93
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,320
Xi'er,

94
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,470
Shaoyu,

95
00:10:33,520 --> 00:10:35,110
why are you doing this to me?

96
00:10:36,710 --> 00:10:38,870
My lover,

97
00:10:40,470 --> 00:10:41,990
my buddy,

98
00:10:44,630 --> 00:10:45,470
why?

99
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:52,200
Chen,

100
00:10:52,950 --> 00:10:54,520
Shaoyu and I were together

101
00:10:54,950 --> 00:10:57,590
before you came into the picture.

102
00:10:58,630 --> 00:11:00,870
I pretended to love you

103
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:02,750
just so I could use you.

104
00:11:11,350 --> 00:11:13,200
I was going to use you as my stepping stone.

105
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:14,800
I hadn't bargained on

106
00:11:15,160 --> 00:11:17,080
you having it in you.

107
00:11:17,710 --> 00:11:19,230
You helped me expand my area of influence

108
00:11:19,350 --> 00:11:21,470
and build the Tianwu Empire.

109
00:11:21,830 --> 00:11:23,400
All those years of buddying up to you,

110
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:25,590
it all paid off.

111
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:28,520
I even had to watch

112
00:11:28,950 --> 00:11:30,200
you and Xi'er getting all lovey-dovey

113
00:11:30,680 --> 00:11:32,160
day after day.

114
00:11:45,630 --> 00:11:47,110
Being around you

115
00:11:47,110 --> 00:11:48,680
made me sick.

116
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:52,080
Shaoyu and I have a deal.

117
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:55,200
When we become
Martial Emperors of the Nine Heavens,

118
00:11:55,800 --> 00:11:58,110
it'll be the time of your death.

119
00:11:58,630 --> 00:11:59,520
And then

120
00:11:59,710 --> 00:12:02,870
I can go back to Shaoyu
without having to answer to anybody.

121
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:07,990
Chen,

122
00:12:08,710 --> 00:12:09,870
I hate to admit it,

123
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,710
but you are quite something

124
00:12:12,350 --> 00:12:14,320
to become a legend in the Martial Domain

125
00:12:14,590 --> 00:12:16,110
without any help.

126
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:24,280
Too bad…

127
00:12:26,040 --> 00:12:26,750
you're going to

128
00:12:26,990 --> 00:12:28,710
die here today.

129
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,400
As a sacrificial offering at my altar.

130
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:34,110
But…

131
00:12:34,470 --> 00:12:36,320
I can let you live

132
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:38,630
for the sake of our years of "brotherhood."

133
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:41,280
As long as you give me this one thing.

134
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:44,520
You took everything away from me.

135
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:47,630
I have nothing more to give you.

136
00:12:47,950 --> 00:12:49,560
You spent days training behind closed doors.

137
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:50,520
I'd imagine

138
00:12:50,750 --> 00:12:52,160
you were studying the divine artifact

139
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:55,040
you had brought back from the Forbidden Place.

140
00:12:55,560 --> 00:12:56,950
Leave it to me,

141
00:12:57,830 --> 00:12:59,520
and I'll spare your life.

142
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:11,280
I discovered

143
00:13:12,870 --> 00:13:14,280
the secrets of the universe,

144
00:13:15,990 --> 00:13:17,560
but failed to look through human nature.

145
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,320
For half of my life,

146
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,950
I've been fighting my destiny.

147
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:26,350
I never would have thought

148
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:30,080
it would end up like this.

149
00:13:32,800 --> 00:13:33,800
Shaoyu,

150
00:13:34,870 --> 00:13:36,470
you still don't get me.

151
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:38,950
As much as I want to

152
00:13:40,830 --> 00:13:41,680
live a good long life,

153
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:46,280
I am never afraid to die.

154
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:49,710
Look out!

155
00:14:19,950 --> 00:14:20,750
I won't

156
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:21,710
let you die so easily.

157
00:14:21,950 --> 00:14:22,990
And when you do die,

158
00:14:22,990 --> 00:14:24,680
I will destroy your soul

159
00:14:24,680 --> 00:14:26,350
so you can never be reborn as a human!

160
00:14:38,460 --> 00:14:41,620
[Qin Residence, King of Might's home,
the Xuan Kingdom]

161
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:45,520
Chen.

162
00:14:51,830 --> 00:14:52,680
[Qin Chen, King of Might's grandson]
Chen?

163
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:54,220
[Qin Chen, King of Might's grandson]

164
00:15:10,230 --> 00:15:11,350
What happened to me…?

165
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:16,870
Chen, you're finally awake.

166
00:15:23,350 --> 00:15:24,320
Where am I?

167
00:15:26,350 --> 00:15:27,440
My boy, I really thought

168
00:15:28,870 --> 00:15:30,350
you were never going to wake up.

169
00:15:34,830 --> 00:15:35,560
Mother?

170
00:15:41,400 --> 00:15:43,440
How were you all beat up?

171
00:15:43,870 --> 00:15:45,230
[Qin Yuechi, King of Might's daughter]
I heard people in your academy talking.

172
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:47,400
Did you really fight a duel with Wei Zhen?

173
00:15:47,870 --> 00:15:49,470
How could he have done this to you?

174
00:15:50,350 --> 00:15:52,320
He clearly wanted you dead.

175
00:15:58,320 --> 00:15:59,230
Don't kill me.

176
00:16:15,040 --> 00:16:15,800
Chen,

177
00:16:16,040 --> 00:16:16,950
what's wrong?

178
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:19,280
[I don't know what's happening right now.]

179
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:23,080
[I seem to have had a really long dream.]

180
00:16:25,040 --> 00:16:28,920
[And it was so vivid, as if it was real.]

181
00:16:30,230 --> 00:16:32,040
[Shangguan Xi'er…]

182
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:35,470
[Feng Shaoyu…]

183
00:16:37,040 --> 00:16:38,320
[Who are they?]

184
00:16:39,470 --> 00:16:43,230
[It feels like some kind of kismet,]

185
00:16:44,160 --> 00:16:46,560
[which planted those memories in my mind.]

186
00:16:46,560 --> 00:16:48,110
Chen, is everything okay?

187
00:16:50,350 --> 00:16:51,830
I'm fine.

188
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:54,200
You were out for three days.

189
00:16:54,590 --> 00:16:55,950
I was so worried.

190
00:16:56,080 --> 00:16:57,710
Do not ever behave recklessly like this,

191
00:16:57,710 --> 00:16:58,680
you hear me?

192
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:00,470
If you…

193
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:04,110
If you had died,

194
00:17:05,560 --> 00:17:06,960
I never would've been able to

195
00:17:08,150 --> 00:17:09,280
bear the pain alone.

196
00:17:12,390 --> 00:17:13,630
Yes…

197
00:17:15,670 --> 00:17:16,480
Mother.

198
00:17:22,080 --> 00:17:23,000
Chen.

199
00:17:25,150 --> 00:17:26,910
Chen, are you all right?

200
00:17:31,390 --> 00:17:32,280
Yeah.

201
00:17:38,430 --> 00:17:39,870
Drink this potion.

202
00:17:40,150 --> 00:17:41,390
It'll help your body recover.

203
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,630
[Mother had been known as
the most beautiful woman]

204
00:17:55,150 --> 00:17:56,760
[in the Xuan Kingdom in her day.]

205
00:17:57,480 --> 00:18:00,280
[Secretly admired by countless noblemen
and aristocrats from the Capitol.]

206
00:18:01,320 --> 00:18:04,110
[Matchmakers bearing gifts
were scrambling to get to her.]

207
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:07,190
[The reigning emperor]

208
00:18:07,190 --> 00:18:08,800
[even wanted to acquire her as his concubine]

209
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:11,080
[after hearing what a stunner she was.]

210
00:18:13,390 --> 00:18:14,560
[And that was when]

211
00:18:15,560 --> 00:18:17,150
[she decided to run away from home.]

212
00:18:17,910 --> 00:18:20,040
[She vanished into thin air.]

213
00:18:30,280 --> 00:18:31,280
[Three years later,]

214
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,590
[she returned home]

215
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:36,760
[with a baby in her arms.]

216
00:18:38,150 --> 00:18:39,430
[Being an unmarried mother]
Miss Yuechi has returned.

217
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:40,350
Miss Yuechi has returned!

218
00:18:40,350 --> 00:18:41,870
[is seen as a huge embarrassment]

219
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:44,020
[by all of the Tianwu Continent.]
Miss Yuechi has returned.

220
00:18:44,100 --> 00:18:44,560
Mr. Qin!

221
00:18:44,560 --> 00:18:46,240
[A woman of loose morals, they call it.]
Miss Yuechi has returned!

222
00:18:47,940 --> 00:18:48,320
Miss Yuechi.

223
00:18:48,320 --> 00:18:50,630
[If my grandfather hadn't stood his ground]
What is Miss Yuechi doing back here?

224
00:18:50,630 --> 00:18:52,240
[and took my mother and me in]

225
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:54,080
[in the name of preserving the bloodline,]
She has a baby with her.

226
00:18:54,630 --> 00:18:58,320
[my mother and I
would have long been kicked out,]

227
00:18:58,960 --> 00:19:00,280
[living homeless on the street.]

228
00:19:10,800 --> 00:19:11,520
Chen,

229
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:13,870
your bloodline

230
00:19:14,560 --> 00:19:16,150
wasn't awakened this time,

231
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:18,670
but it doesn't matter.

232
00:19:19,350 --> 00:19:20,760
There might still be a chance.

233
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:22,910
My bloodline wasn't awakened?

234
00:19:38,760 --> 00:19:40,870
It doesn't matter

235
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:42,280
if you can't be a skilled fighter, son.

236
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:44,150
I will always be there

237
00:19:45,350 --> 00:19:47,080
to protect you.

238
00:19:51,670 --> 00:19:52,390
Mother,

239
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:54,000
don't worry.

240
00:19:54,560 --> 00:19:56,350
I can handle setbacks.

241
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:01,150
All right,

242
00:20:02,390 --> 00:20:03,800
I'm relieved to hear that.

243
00:20:17,870 --> 00:20:19,150
Miss Yuechi,

244
00:20:19,280 --> 00:20:21,350
took you long enough.

245
00:20:22,560 --> 00:20:23,320
Yanzhi,

246
00:20:23,430 --> 00:20:24,560
Chen just woke up.

247
00:20:24,590 --> 00:20:25,870
He's still weak.

248
00:20:25,910 --> 00:20:27,040
You might startle him.

249
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:32,000
Huh.

250
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:34,590
You're awake, Master Chen.

251
00:20:34,590 --> 00:20:36,080
Wonderful news.

252
00:20:36,320 --> 00:20:37,280
What do you want?

253
00:20:37,870 --> 00:20:39,630
Get over yourself, Master Chen.

254
00:20:39,630 --> 00:20:41,080
I didn't come here for you.

255
00:20:42,280 --> 00:20:43,080
Miss Yuechi,

256
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:44,560
[Yanzhi, a maid at Qin Residence]
I suppose you haven't forgotten

257
00:20:44,630 --> 00:20:45,960
the deal you made with Ms. Zhao?

258
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:53,520
Chen,

259
00:20:54,390 --> 00:20:55,800
rest well.

260
00:20:56,150 --> 00:20:57,390
I have somewhere to be.

261
00:20:58,520 --> 00:20:59,080
Mother,

262
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:00,800
where are you going?

263
00:21:01,040 --> 00:21:01,830
I'm coming with you.

264
00:21:04,150 --> 00:21:05,190
Oh, monkey.

265
00:21:05,670 --> 00:21:07,390
I'm not leaving the house.

266
00:21:07,560 --> 00:21:09,150
Go get some rest.

267
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:10,390
I will

268
00:21:10,670 --> 00:21:11,760
be right back.

269
00:21:11,760 --> 00:21:12,350
Mother,

270
00:21:13,080 --> 00:21:14,040
what have you and Ms. Zhao agreed on?

271
00:21:14,280 --> 00:21:15,910
Fill me in.

272
00:21:18,040 --> 00:21:20,040
For someone at death's door,

273
00:21:20,430 --> 00:21:21,830
you sure ask a lot of questions.

274
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:24,630
I'll be honest with you.

275
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:26,830
Your mother agreed to Ms. Zhao's request

276
00:21:26,910 --> 00:21:28,760
to meet with Lord Qi today.

277
00:21:28,870 --> 00:21:29,480
Lord Qi

278
00:21:29,630 --> 00:21:31,190
is already in the living room waiting

279
00:21:31,240 --> 00:21:32,390
for your mother.

280
00:21:32,800 --> 00:21:34,590
You'd better not get in the way.

281
00:21:34,870 --> 00:21:36,830
Lord Qi? You mean Zhao Qirui?

282
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:42,190
What is Zhao Feng up to?

283
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:45,800
Why is she asking you to see that villain?

284
00:21:47,040 --> 00:21:47,590
You,

285
00:21:48,110 --> 00:21:49,110
get out of here.

286
00:21:49,630 --> 00:21:51,350
What did you just say?

287
00:21:54,320 --> 00:21:55,430
That's a spoiled brat you got there,

288
00:21:55,870 --> 00:21:57,190
Miss Yuechi.

289
00:21:57,830 --> 00:21:59,040
You agreed to meeting with Lord Qi.

290
00:21:59,080 --> 00:22:00,800
You made that promise.

291
00:22:00,960 --> 00:22:02,190
Now you're going back on your word?

292
00:22:02,280 --> 00:22:03,390
That's utter nonsense.

293
00:22:04,080 --> 00:22:05,760
That unpleasant person

294
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:07,800
made several attempts to see my mother,

295
00:22:08,150 --> 00:22:09,560
all of which were declined.

296
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,560
My mother couldn't have agreed to meet him.

297
00:22:12,040 --> 00:22:13,830
Well, why don't you ask her yourself?

298
00:22:17,670 --> 00:22:18,590
Chen,

299
00:22:19,190 --> 00:22:20,320
you have just regained consciousness.

300
00:22:20,910 --> 00:22:22,080
I'd hate for you to overwhelm yourself.

301
00:22:23,150 --> 00:22:23,910
It's…

302
00:22:24,590 --> 00:22:26,150
just a meeting, nothing more.

303
00:22:27,320 --> 00:22:28,350
I'll be fine.

304
00:22:29,590 --> 00:22:30,240
But Mother,

305
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:32,280
by doing that,

306
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:33,910
you're tempting fate.

307
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:36,430
Pretty bold of you to say that.

308
00:22:37,280 --> 00:22:39,390
You slipped into a coma after a duel.

309
00:22:39,670 --> 00:22:41,480
You were literally on your deathbed.

310
00:22:41,910 --> 00:22:43,560
Your mother shamelessly

311
00:22:43,560 --> 00:22:45,560
kneeled outside Ms. Zhao's room all night,

312
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,520
begging for a wake-up pill.

313
00:22:47,630 --> 00:22:48,520
Ms. Zhao was kind enough to…

314
00:22:48,560 --> 00:22:49,520
Shut your mouth.

315
00:22:50,960 --> 00:22:52,830
Ms. Zhao promised me

316
00:22:53,390 --> 00:22:55,280
she wouldn't tell anyone about it.

317
00:22:56,280 --> 00:22:57,870
[I can't believe
Mother suffered such humiliation]

318
00:22:58,430 --> 00:23:00,590
[to save me.]

319
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:02,190
Miss Yuechi…

320
00:23:02,190 --> 00:23:02,870
Enough.

321
00:23:04,150 --> 00:23:05,000
I'll go with you.

322
00:23:05,430 --> 00:23:06,110
No.

323
00:23:07,910 --> 00:23:09,000
We're not going anywhere.

324
00:23:09,430 --> 00:23:10,480
From now on,

325
00:23:11,150 --> 00:23:13,240
I will not let anyone
treat you like a doormat anymore.

326
00:23:14,630 --> 00:23:15,480
As for you,

327
00:23:16,240 --> 00:23:17,560
get out of my face, now.

328
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:21,000
Oh, please. Being addressed as "Master Chen"

329
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,390
doesn't mean you are my master.

330
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:23,150
Mind your manners.

331
00:23:23,800 --> 00:23:25,000
Need I remind you that

332
00:23:25,280 --> 00:23:26,830
you're just a maid here at the house?

333
00:23:27,870 --> 00:23:28,830
Wow.

334
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:30,870
Are you trying to take me down a peg?

335
00:23:31,560 --> 00:23:33,590
Ms. Zhao already knew
you wouldn't keep your side of the bargain.

336
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:35,240
Somebody,

337
00:23:37,520 --> 00:23:39,240
take Miss Yuechi to the living room.

338
00:23:39,560 --> 00:23:41,630
We mustn't keep Ms. Zhao and our guests waiting.

339
00:23:42,280 --> 00:23:43,960
Apologies, Miss Yuechi.

340
00:23:49,280 --> 00:23:50,480
Nobody touches my mother.

341
00:23:50,590 --> 00:23:51,080
You…

342
00:23:51,150 --> 00:23:52,000
You're such a piece of human garbage.

343
00:23:52,430 --> 00:23:53,910
Just so you know,
you're not the boss around here.

344
00:23:54,870 --> 00:23:56,350
Get Miss Yuechi to the living room now.

345
00:23:56,670 --> 00:23:57,480
Unless you're ready to bear the consequences

346
00:23:57,560 --> 00:23:58,870
of pissing off Ms. Zhao!

347
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:00,760
Master Chen,

348
00:24:02,320 --> 00:24:04,040
