349
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:05,670
If you insist on standing in the way,

350
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:07,560
I'm afraid we're going to
have to do it the hard way.

351
00:24:07,760 --> 00:24:08,760
Sure, go ahead.

352
00:24:09,110 --> 00:24:10,280
If you have a death wish.

353
00:24:10,560 --> 00:24:12,480
Let's see which one of you
has the balls to do it.

354
00:24:13,590 --> 00:24:15,830
You silly cocks on your own dunghill.

355
00:24:16,150 --> 00:24:18,800
I could banish you three thousand miles away
in accordance with the household rules.

356
00:24:19,110 --> 00:24:20,590
And you'll spend the rest of your life in exile.

357
00:24:23,240 --> 00:24:24,110
Yanzhi,

358
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:26,390
Master Chen is part of the Qin family.

359
00:24:26,590 --> 00:24:28,110
If he makes a big thing out of this,

360
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:30,240
we, as the servants, are in big trouble.

361
00:24:33,910 --> 00:24:34,720
Oh.

362
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:37,080
Did I hear
someone say something about being in exile?

363
00:24:38,000 --> 00:24:38,870
Ms. Zhao.

364
00:24:39,320 --> 00:24:40,760
This was too simple a task to screw up, Yanzhi.

365
00:24:40,910 --> 00:24:42,350
I taught you better than this.

366
00:24:46,080 --> 00:24:47,150
It's my fault, Ms. Zhao.

367
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:48,560
I'm ready to take my punishment.

368
00:24:50,150 --> 00:24:51,430
[Zhao Feng, Qin Yuanhong's wife]
Step aside.

369
00:24:51,830 --> 00:24:53,000
You're embarrassing me.

370
00:24:53,110 --> 00:24:53,760
Absolutely.

371
00:24:56,460 --> 00:24:58,870
[Zhao Qirui, Lord Qi of the Xuan Kingdom]

372
00:24:58,870 --> 00:25:00,040
Yuechi,

373
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,320
it's been a while.

374
00:25:02,830 --> 00:25:04,110
Would you look at that?

375
00:25:04,320 --> 00:25:06,150
My sweet nephew was out for a few days,

376
00:25:06,150 --> 00:25:07,670
and suddenly he's a brave heart.

377
00:25:08,110 --> 00:25:09,830
You threatened to exile my people.

378
00:25:11,280 --> 00:25:13,150
You have a lot of ambition, don't you?

379
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:14,760
Ms. Zhao,

380
00:25:15,480 --> 00:25:17,040
Chen is still young.

381
00:25:17,040 --> 00:25:18,110
He said things he didn't mean

382
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:18,960
in the heat of the moment.

383
00:25:19,590 --> 00:25:20,630
Please,

384
00:25:21,080 --> 00:25:22,240
let him off.

385
00:25:22,870 --> 00:25:24,110
Young?

386
00:25:24,560 --> 00:25:26,280
As part of the Qin family,

387
00:25:26,280 --> 00:25:27,910
he should have devoted himself to his studies.

388
00:25:27,910 --> 00:25:29,630
Instead, he got into a fight at the academy.

389
00:25:29,870 --> 00:25:31,350
And not to mention all those mean words he used

390
00:25:31,350 --> 00:25:32,390
to humiliate the helpers earlier.

391
00:25:33,080 --> 00:25:34,870
You broke the household rules.

392
00:25:35,150 --> 00:25:36,670
What should be the punishment for that, hmm?

393
00:25:36,870 --> 00:25:37,760
Chen…

394
00:25:38,150 --> 00:25:39,190
he didn't mean it.

395
00:25:39,350 --> 00:25:40,960
You should be the one

396
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:42,630
to get punished.

397
00:25:42,630 --> 00:25:43,280
You…

398
00:25:49,040 --> 00:25:50,870
Despite being the lady of the house,

399
00:25:51,190 --> 00:25:52,350
you wink at the servants'

400
00:25:52,350 --> 00:25:54,520
mistreatment of the family members.

401
00:25:55,320 --> 00:25:57,520
So much for the household rules.

402
00:25:59,320 --> 00:26:01,390
You even get involved with

403
00:26:01,390 --> 00:26:03,280
a notorious rake in the Capital.

404
00:26:04,150 --> 00:26:06,150
You call that virtuous?

405
00:26:07,080 --> 00:26:07,430
Uh,

406
00:26:07,560 --> 00:26:08,390
I came today

407
00:26:08,390 --> 00:26:10,390
to visit your mother.

408
00:26:10,560 --> 00:26:11,960
So why do you need to be so rude?

409
00:26:12,110 --> 00:26:13,350
That's ridiculous.

410
00:26:13,760 --> 00:26:15,590
Lord Qi is my brother.

411
00:26:15,590 --> 00:26:16,480
That's right.

412
00:26:16,910 --> 00:26:17,670
Well, uh,

413
00:26:17,670 --> 00:26:20,480
Ms. Zhao's ancestors had royal ancestry.

414
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,560
Her referring to me as her brother;

415
00:26:21,560 --> 00:26:22,630
I don't see anything wrong with it.

416
00:26:23,080 --> 00:26:23,760
I don't think I said

417
00:26:23,760 --> 00:26:25,390
it was you, did I?

418
00:26:25,870 --> 00:26:26,350
Uh…

419
00:26:27,870 --> 00:26:29,320
Now that you mention it,

420
00:26:29,320 --> 00:26:30,560
I'll make this simple.

421
00:26:31,190 --> 00:26:32,630
Even as siblings,

422
00:26:33,190 --> 00:26:34,830
having secret rendezvous

423
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:37,000
is somewhat of a taboo, no?

424
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:38,800
Uh…

425
00:26:38,800 --> 00:26:39,760
Ms. Zhao,

426
00:26:40,430 --> 00:26:43,480
as Madam of Gaoming,
a title granted by His Majesty,

427
00:26:43,910 --> 00:26:46,240
