a role model for other women.

428
00:26:46,870 --> 00:26:48,080
And act with integrity.

429
00:26:49,000 --> 00:26:50,670
If this gets out,

430
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:53,910
our family could be toppled
from our position in the kingdom.

431
00:26:55,910 --> 00:26:57,320
You…

432
00:26:57,760 --> 00:26:59,590
you're out of your mind.

433
00:26:59,590 --> 00:27:00,350
Somebody,

434
00:27:00,350 --> 00:27:01,520
get him!

435
00:27:01,520 --> 00:27:02,960
You won't lay a hand on him.

436
00:27:03,190 --> 00:27:03,760
Sorry,

437
00:27:03,960 --> 00:27:04,560
Miss Yuechi.

438
00:27:12,590 --> 00:27:13,480
Chen,

439
00:27:13,830 --> 00:27:15,480
how dare you fight back.

440
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:17,430
You asked for this.

441
00:27:17,720 --> 00:27:18,430
Somebody,

442
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:20,280
Master Chen will be disciplined
in accordance with the household rules.

443
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:22,040
He has to be made an example of!

444
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:26,670
The audacity!

445
00:27:26,830 --> 00:27:28,040
Drop your sword!

446
00:27:28,760 --> 00:27:29,590
Drop my sword?

447
00:27:30,280 --> 00:27:30,870
Chen, no!

448
00:27:41,430 --> 00:27:42,280
Don't worry, Mother.

449
00:27:42,630 --> 00:27:43,590
I've got this.

450
00:27:44,590 --> 00:27:46,520
Don't push your luck.

451
00:27:46,830 --> 00:27:48,320
Right back at you,

452
00:27:49,040 --> 00:27:49,910
Zhao Feng.

453
00:28:07,190 --> 00:28:07,560
What…

454
00:28:08,590 --> 00:28:10,670
Take advantage of my mother again,

455
00:28:11,280 --> 00:28:13,110
and that's what you'll end up with.

456
00:28:15,760 --> 00:28:16,560
Ms. Zhao,

457
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:19,720
I thought you had made
the arrangements with Yuechi.

458
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:21,280
Lord Qi,

459
00:28:21,280 --> 00:28:22,350
I can explain.

460
00:28:22,350 --> 00:28:23,320
Save your breath.

461
00:28:27,760 --> 00:28:28,670
Yuechi,

462
00:28:29,630 --> 00:28:30,720
what happened today

463
00:28:31,190 --> 00:28:33,110
was completely unintentional.

464
00:28:33,590 --> 00:28:34,560
I've had feelings for you

465
00:28:34,800 --> 00:28:36,110
for years.

466
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:38,350
Thought you should know.

467
00:28:38,670 --> 00:28:39,960
Have some self-respect, Your Highness.

468
00:28:40,560 --> 00:28:41,240
Yuechi.

469
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:42,000
Shut your mouth.

470
00:28:43,190 --> 00:28:44,630
One more step,

471
00:28:45,800 --> 00:28:47,040
and you die.

472
00:28:47,870 --> 00:28:48,630
Qin!

473
00:28:49,320 --> 00:28:50,720
Don't just stand there gawking.

474
00:28:51,040 --> 00:28:51,480
Absolutely.

475
00:28:55,340 --> 00:28:57,800
[Qin Yong, butler of Qin Residence]

476
00:28:57,800 --> 00:29:00,240
Execute him right here and now!

477
00:29:00,600 --> 00:29:01,400
Master Chen,

478
00:29:02,360 --> 00:29:03,880
you might as well give it up

479
00:29:03,880 --> 00:29:05,880
