480
00:29:06,320 --> 00:29:08,120
You want me to back down?

481
00:29:08,770 --> 00:29:10,880
Go ahead and make me.

482
00:29:13,290 --> 00:29:14,400
Well, okay,

483
00:29:14,690 --> 00:29:16,530
