494
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:43,870
Haven't you made enough fuss?

495
00:29:43,870 --> 00:29:45,240
I didn't want any of this.

496
00:29:45,240 --> 00:29:46,350
It's all because of this little…

497
00:29:46,350 --> 00:29:46,760
he…

498
00:29:46,760 --> 00:29:48,110
He is your nephew.

499
00:29:48,790 --> 00:29:50,110
If he is worthless,

500
00:29:50,110 --> 00:29:51,550
then what does that make us?

501
00:29:52,070 --> 00:29:54,200
You need to start behaving
like the lady of the house!

502
00:29:57,240 --> 00:29:58,000
Lord Qi,

503
00:29:58,720 --> 00:30:00,590
I'm sorry you had to witness this.

504
00:30:01,070 --> 00:30:02,280
Their behaviors were extremely inappropriate.

505
00:30:02,550 --> 00:30:03,870
Oh, don't get me started.

506
00:30:04,350 --> 00:30:05,150
See for yourself

507
00:30:05,150 --> 00:30:06,680
