510
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:17,000
Sorry, Yuechi,

511
00:30:17,390 --> 00:30:18,760
I didn't mean to scare you.

512
00:30:19,150 --> 00:30:20,070
I hope you're okay.

513
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:28,790
Yuanhong,

514
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:29,960
I demand

515
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,280
