517
00:30:32,870 --> 00:30:33,960
Yes, Lord Qi,

518
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:36,310
I will have an explanation for you.

519
00:30:36,720 --> 00:30:40,070
However, I suppose
you wouldn't want it to get out that

520
00:30:40,070 --> 00:30:42,590
