521
00:30:43,550 --> 00:30:45,790
I have other things to attend to.

522
00:30:45,790 --> 00:30:47,000
I won't keep you any longer, Lord Qi.

523
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,040
Qin Yuanhong, look at you,

524
00:30:49,070 --> 00:30:51,040
being all high and mighty.

525
00:30:52,070 --> 00:30:53,040
I will get even with you

526
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:54,680
for what happened today!

527
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:56,390
Hmph!

528
00:30:57,590 --> 00:30:58,630
Show yourself out.

529
00:30:58,830 --> 00:31:00,000
Lord Qi.

